2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the use of orthogonal space-time block codes in pico-cellular MIMO networks, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper may be relevant to the study of MIMO channels in social and information networks. 
4. cs.COMM (Communication and Networking) - The paper deals with communication over a MIMO channel, which is a core topic in communication and networking. 
5. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper may be relevant to the study of multiagent systems that use MIMO channels for communication.
